<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">They are in this, but one of them doesn&apos;t show up until the middle of the story, the other until nearly the end. However, if you&apos;re paying attention, <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">They are in this, but one of them doesn't show up until the middle of the story, the other until nearly the end. However, if you're paying attention, you can actually figure out where they are much sooner than that.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
